{"word":"ταξιάρχης","slug":"ταξιάρχης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n102374\" key=\"tacia/rxhs\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ταξῐάρχ-ης</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ου</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, less common form of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ταξίαρχος</foreign>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg008:182:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.\">A.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Fr.\">Fr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">182.1</biblScope> </bibl> (acc. pl. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-ας</foreign>), <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hippod.</author> </bibl> ap. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Stob.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.1.94</biblScope> </bibl> (nom. pl. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-αι</foreign>); gen. pl. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-έων</foreign> is <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.l. in</abbr> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:99\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.99</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:53\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.53</biblScope></bibl>, but he uses nom. pl. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ταξίαρχοι</foreign> (v. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ταξίαρχος</foreign>)<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">; ταξιαρχῶν</foreign> is so accented in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:755e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">755e</biblScope></bibl>, but acc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ταξιάρχους</foreign> occurs ibid.; <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">τ</itype>. used as a nickname, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:latinLit:phi0474.phi057.perseus-lat1:16:11:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Cic.\">Cic.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.11.3</biblScope> </bibl>; cf. <sense id=\"n102374.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ταξίαρχος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:latinLit:phi0474.phi057.perseus-lat1:1:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.2</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> and <bibl n=\"urn:cts:latinLit:phi0474.phi057.perseus-lat1:1:3b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3b</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:latinLit:phi0474.phi057.perseus-lat1:1:3c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3c</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}